Menulis Dan Membaca File

==============================

Membuat File :

<?php
$pesan="Ini hasil membuat file melalui PHP";
file_put_contents("file.txt",$pesan);
?>

===============================

Membaca File :

<?php
$pesan="Ini hasil membuat file melalui PHP";
file_put_contents("file.txt",$pesan);
$isi_file = file_get_contents("file.txt");
echo $isi_file;
?>

======================
